Package ohos.ivihardware.cluster

Provides signal access functions dedicated to clusters, including cluster property definition, sensor value retrieval and subscription, and actuator value retrieval, setting, and subscription.

Using this package, applications can obtain cluster properties, such as the cluster brand, model, and fuel type.

Applications can also obtain signals generated by the cluster body, chassis, drivetrain, cabin, and on-board diagnostics (OBD) system.

To access these signals, applications must apply for the corresponding signal access permissions, for example, the permission to read signals from the cluster body.
